{
  "text": "TSDs. BLAST2SEQUENCES [CITATION_1] and DOTTER [CITATION_2] computer programs were used to find matching substrings at least 6-bp long. One mismatch was allowed for repeats >11-bp long. A pair of short direct repeats was considered a TSD pair if the 5\u0408 TSD adjoined the 5\u0408 end of the L1 element and the 3\u0408 TSD immediately followed a poly(A) tail.",
